OL,3,CEvidence suggests link between
OL,4,C'forever chemicals' and some health
OL,5,Cconditions
OL,7,FIt's the second report from the PFAS
OL,8,FScientific Advisory Panel into the
OL,9,Feffects of the chemical on people's
OL,10,Fhealth, released at a public meeting
OL,11,Fon Tuesday 26 November.
OL,13,FCampaigners hope this is a step
OL,14,Ftowards understanding the health
OL,15,Feffects of PFAS after the chemical
OL,16,Fmade its way into private Jersey bore-
OL,17,Fholes in the 1990s.
