OL,5,Cconditions
OL,7,FJeremy Snowdon says: "The last 10 to
OL,8,F20 years, I've just felt as if I'm
OL,9,Fbanging my head against a brick wall,
OL,10,Ftrying to get things done, and at last
OL,11,Fwe see the first glimmer of something
OL,12,Fhappening."
OL,14,FPFAS is a long-lasting chemical that
OL,15,Fcan be found globally, with scientists
OL,16,Fstill piecing together what effects it
OL,17,Fcan have on people's health.
