OL,3,CEvidence suggests link between
OL,4,C'forever chemicals' and some health
OL,5,Cconditions
OL,7,FIn 1991, PFAS was used in fire-
OL,8,Ffighting foams at Jersey Airport for
OL,9,Ftraining, which leaked into private
OL,10,Fbore-hole water supplies.
OL,12,FIn 2022, blood tests from 88 people
OL,13,Fwho lived close to the airport found
OL,14,F'higher than expected' levels of PFAS
OL,15,Fin their systems.
OL,17,FGraeme Farmer took part in the testing
OL,18,Fprogram and was later diagnosed with
OL,19,Fblood cancer.
