OL,7,FHe believes drinking water in the area
OL,8,Faround the airport has caused his
OL,9,Fcondition, but there is currently no
OL,10,Fscientific evidence to prove this.
OL,12,FGraeme explains: "There is no cure for
OL,13,Fwhat I have. Hopefully, they can
OL,14,Fmaintain it and hopefully, I'll be an
OL,15,Fold man, but you can never know what
OL,16,Fis around the corner. So that is a
OL,17,Fconstant worry."
