OL,5,Cconditions
OL,7,FProfessor Peter Bradley, Jersey's
OL,8,FDirector of Public Health, attended
OL,9,Fthe public meeting and reassured
OL,10,Fislanders that the report shows no
OL,11,Fincreased risk factors for islanders.
OL,13,FHe explains: "The international
OL,14,Fliterature does show that if you are
OL,15,Fexposed to PFAS at a reasonable level,
OL,16,Fwe need to think about some specific
OL,17,Fconditions which may impact your
OL,18,Fhealth.
