OL,7,F"But at the moment, islanders can be
OL,8,Freassured that there is no elevated
OL,9,Frisk because of this report. We've
OL,10,Fjust collected what is known
OL,11,Finternationally at this stage."
OL,13,FThe Government says Jersey's water
OL,14,Fmeets European standards - and that it
OL,15,Fwants to further improve water quality
OL,16,Fover time while doing whatever it
OL,17,Ftakes to resolve the issue for
OL,18,Faffected residents.
